metadata.name: Row Delta 1/1
metadata.description:
Faced with disguised time zones, supernatural alleys and monsters hidden in tagged side streets. Black boots, black skirt, patterned tights and an oversized patchwork decorated racing bomber jacket. In pre-loved condition, mixed shades of red, white and blue printed emblems stand as hand me downs from the last decade.   

Synth Graph: real life full photograph of a group of beautiful tanned 25 year old females posing with luxury fashion streetwear, wearing oversized racing Bomber jacket in black, navy and red, with white and black hair, captured with a Olympus E-M10 III, high resolution, very detailed, highly realistic, new york city and paris vibes. Sampler: klms, steps: 70, scale: 10.
